  Accept: application/json
}

body:json {
  {}
}

docs {
  v1.9.1 (#92 Audi S6 C8) — vehicle wakeup with v1→v2 fallback.
  Premium Audi models return 404 on /vehicle/v1/vehicles/{vin}/vehicleWakeup
  → _post_command auto-falls-back to /vehicle/v2/.../vehicleWakeup.

  Wake counts against the user's daily wake-budget (3/day soft-cap
  since v1.12.0). 5-min cooldown per VIN since v1.13.0.

  Implementation: VWEUClient.command_wake() in cariad/api/vw_eu.py:321.
  Audi inherits.
}
